&lt;p&gt;Azure Cognitive Services provides a straightforward way to deploy OpenAI models, including powerful text-to-speech capabilities. In this guide, Iâ€™ll demonstrate how to deploy a text-to-speech model using Azure CLI commands.&lt;/p&gt;
